http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/New-autopsy-block-at-AIMS/article14596322.ece

An autopsy block with state-of-the-art facilities, viewing gallery, cold storage and separate rooms for police inquest, relatives of the deceased and visitors was inaugurated at the Amrita Institute of Medical Sciences (AIMS) on Sunday by Arul R.B. Krishna, Deputy Commissioner of Police (Law and Order and Traffic). — Staff Reporter